# 🧠 Viva Questions (VERY IMPORTANT)

### ❓ What is a Pod?

👉 Smallest unit in Kubernetes (runs containers)

---

### ❓ What is Deployment?

👉 Manages replicas of pods

---

### ❓ What is kubectl?

👉 CLI tool to control Kubernetes

---

### ❓ What is NodePort?

👉 Exposes service on a port accessible outside cluster

---

### ❓ Why YAML?

👉 Infrastructure as Code (declarative config)

